<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-black dark:text-white p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8 rounded-lg">
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
      <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Il <strong>congiuntivo</strong> è il modo dell'incertezza, del desiderio, dell'eventualità. Indica un'azione possibile o desiderata, ma non certa; esprime un'opinione o un dubbio. È formato da:
    </p>
    <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 ml-6">
      <p><span class="text-red-500">•</span> <strong>due tempi semplici</strong> → presente, imperfetto;</p>
      <p><span class="text-blue-500">•</span> <strong>due tempi composti</strong> → passato, trapassato.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
      Osserva lo schema del modo congiuntivo e completa le frasi coniugando il verbo <strong>leggere</strong> al tempo indicato.
    </h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full border-collapse">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-100 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/50">
            <th class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 font-bold">Tempi semplici</th>
            <th class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 font-bold">Tempi composti</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-4">
              <p class="font-semibold text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 mb-2">Presente</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                <span>Spero che Lele</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="legga" data-correct-answer="legga">
                <span>il libro.</span>
              </div>
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-4">
              <p class="font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 mb-2">Passato</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                <span>Spero che Lele</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="abbia letto" data-correct-answer="abbia letto">
                <span>il libro.</span>
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/20">
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-4">
              <p class="font-semibold text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 mb-2">Imperfetto</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                <span>Speravo che Lele</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="leggesse" data-correct-answer="leggesse">
                <span>il libro.</span>
              </div>
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-4">
              <p class="font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 mb-2">Trapassato</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                <span>Speravo che Lele</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="avesse letto" data-correct-answer="avesse letto">
                <span>il libro.</span>
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2: Underline simple and compound tenses -->
  <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="true">
    <h2 class="font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
      Sottolinea tempi semplici<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-red-300 rounded ml-1 cursor-pointer" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span> e tempi composti<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-blue-300 rounded ml-1 cursor-pointer" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span>.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Ci sembra che il dottore <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">abbia dato</span> una bella spiegazione.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Se Pablo <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">avesse saputo</span> che venivi anche tu, ci avrebbe raggiunto.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Che gioia sarebbe se tu <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">vincessi</span> una medaglia!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Non mi va bene che <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">passiate</span> tutto il giorno davanti alla TV.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 3: Highlight correct form -->
  <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="multiple-choice">
    <h2 class="font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">3</span>
      Evidenzia la forma verbale corretta.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <div class="rounded-lg p-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Pensavo che Martina
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1 cursor-pointer"><input type="radio" name="ex3_1" value="faccia" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">faccia</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1 cursor-pointer"><input type="radio" name="ex3_1" value="facesse" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">facesse</span></label>
          più tardi.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg p-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Mi pare che tu
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1 cursor-pointer"><input type="radio" name="ex3_2" value="abbia dormito" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">abbia dormito</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1 cursor-pointer"><input type="radio" name="ex3_2" value="avessi dormito" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">avessi dormito</span></label>
          troppo poco: hai le occhiaie.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg p-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Credo che il signor Rossi
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1 cursor-pointer"><input type="radio" name="ex3_3" value="abbia deciso" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">abbia deciso</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1 cursor-pointer"><input type="radio" name="ex3_3" value="decida" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">decida</span></label>
          di cambiare casa.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg p-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Ora vorrei che
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1 cursor-pointer"><input type="radio" name="ex3_4" value="mangiaste" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">mangiaste</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1 cursor-pointer"><input type="radio" name="ex3_4" value="aveste mangiato" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">aveste mangiato</span></label>
          un po' di frutta.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-lg p-3">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Se
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1 cursor-pointer"><input type="radio" name="ex3_5" value="guardassi" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">guardassi</span></label> /
          <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mx-1 cursor-pointer"><input type="radio" name="ex3_5" value="avessi guardato" class="w-4 h-4"><span class="font-semibold">avessi guardato</span></label>
          meglio, avresti visto anche tu quella macchia.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-right text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
    Esercizi pp. <%= link_to "165", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p165"), class: "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 underline" %>, <%= link_to "166", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p166"), class: "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 underline" %>, <%= link_to "167", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p167"), class: "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 underline" %> e <%= link_to "169", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p169"), class: "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 underline" %>
  </div>

  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
</div>
